emibold text-white","children":"Key Points"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","li","GPT-5.x leads the general AI category with strong math and reasoning metrics.",{"children":"GPT-5.x leads the general AI category with strong math and reasoning metrics."}],["$","li","Claude Opus 4.5/4.6 and Gemini 3.1 Pro remain close challengers in coding and multimodal tasks.",{"children":"Claude Opus 4.5/4.6 and Gemini 3.1 Pro remain close challengers in coding and multimodal tasks."}],["$","li","Rust, Next.js, and Claude Code receive top recognition in their respective categories.",{"children":"Rust, Next.js, and Claude Code receive top recognition in their respective categories."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10 space-y-10","children":[["$","section","What Is New in 2026",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-white","children":"What Is New in 2026"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-zinc-400","children":[["$","p","The 2026 edition introduces refreshed weighting for frontier reasoning, production coding performance, and long-context reliability. The methodology also expands independent review for reproducibility and practical deployment quality.",{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":"The 2026 edition introduces refreshed weighting for frontier reasoning, production coding performance, and long-context reliability. The methodology also expands independent review for reproducibility and practical deployment quality."}],["$","p","This year's rankings prioritize evidence from public benchmark suites and real-world developer workflows, not marketing claims. Every top-ranked system is assessed using a blend of benchmark performance, qualitative expert review, and implementation cost/efficiency factors.",{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":"This year's rankings prioritize evidence from public benchmark suites and real-world developer workflows, not marketing 